I wanted to introduce you to Isaac Montes. He is working on a blueprint for a client and is having some trouble. The SDK produces a blueprint that doesn't seem to work and we're having trouble finding documentation on it. We'd specifically like to know how the BlueprintPageCreateEvent interface is implemented. The SDK creates a line that throws an exception:

